data.description: SELLER OFFERIGNG $4790 TOWARD MORTGAGE BUY DOWN!!!!Experience the Ultimate in Craftsman-Style Living!  Nestled in the picturesque neighborhood of Emerald Cove Villas, this meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath, two-story craftsman-style home, located at 532 Cove Villa Street in Panama City Beach, offers the epitome of modern luxury and convenience! Built in 2021, this property boasts 2,496 square feet of living space and a two-car garage, showcasing a harmonious blend of timeless craftsmanship and contemporary comfort. Discover a thoughtfully designed layout, offering four generously sized bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms, ensuring abundant space for your family. The second floor hosts a spacious game room/bonus room, providing endless opportunities for leisure and entertainment.Enjoy the aesthetic appeal and easy maintenance of vinyl plank flooring that extends throughout the first floor, including common areas, bathrooms, and the laundry room. Plush carpeting graces the upstairs bedrooms for added comfort.  The kitchen is a culinary haven, showcasing white painted cabinetry, and stunning granite countertops. Premium stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, including a smooth top stove, dishwasher, and microwave, elevate your cooking experience.  Situated on the first floor, the primary bedroom offers both privacy and luxury. It features a walk-in closet and a spa-like 5-foot walk-in shower in the attached primary bathroom. This property is equipped with a comprehensive smart home package, featuring Kwikset Keyless entry, an Echo Dot device, a QOLSYS IQ touch panel, and a Skybell doorbell, enhancing your security and convenience.  Step into your private backyard, enclosed by a full privacy fence and gate. You'll also appreciate the gutters and downspouts, as well as the lush landscaping, including three palm trees and two sago palms. This newer construction home translates into significant savings with lower insurance costs, a newer roof, water heater, and more.  Conveniently located near the Hathaway Bridge, this home is just minutes away from the bay, the pristine beaches, the Naval Support Activity Base, and the vibrant heart of Panama City.  This craftsman-style masterpiece effortlessly combines timeless design with modern amenities, creating the perfect place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your own!
